description:
Free Fit is a wearable devices application client software for smart watches, smart bracelet and other intelligent devices, The main functions include as following:
1.Record steps, mileage, calorie consumption, sports track record;
2.Analysis of daily sleep data, monitoring the quality of sleep;
3.Support calls, text messages, WeChat, QQ ,Facebook,Twitter content pushing and reminder;
4.Clock, alarm clock, anti-lost, sedentary reminder, remote camera and the other function;
5.Support sports and health information sharing on the micro-blog, Twitter, Facebook.

Warm Tips: Install this software must be above ios 9.0, The phone must supports Bluetooth 4.0+.

Disclaimer:
1. The data displayed by the app is provided by devices such as watches and bracelets, and the app is only for recording and sharing.
2. All the health data displayed in the app are not suitable for medical purposes. All health data is for reference only and the data should not be used as a substitute for a medical expert's opinion. To obtain accurate data, please consult your doctor.

License description
1. We will access iPhone Health and synchronize device data to iPhone Health in real time
2. We will access the mobile phone location to get local weather information and synchronize it to the device display
